<h2>Properties</h2>
<h3>share($property, [$property...,] $value)</h3>
<p>Outputs multiple <code>$property</code> values with the same value. For example:</p>

<% code("scss") do %>
// Input:
share(padding-top, padding-bottom, 20px);

// Output:
padding-top: 20px;
padding-bottom: 20px;
<% end %>


<h2>Arrow</h2>
<h3>arrow($size: 10px, $color: inherit, $direction: down)</h3>
<p>Makes a CSS arrow shape. <code>$direction</code> can be one of the following,
and affects the direction the arrow points in:</p>

<ul>
  <li>down (default)</li>
  <li>up</li>
  <li>left</li>
  <li>right</li>
</ul>
